<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>请使用浏览器打开->->->-></title>
    <style>
        *{
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .header {
            width: 100%;
            height: 20%;
            background: #484646e8;
            padding-bottom: 10%;
        }

        .header p {
            padding-top:10%;
            text-align:center;
            color:white;
        }

        .load_box {
            width: 100%;
            height: 600px;
            background-color: #252525d6;
            padding-top: 30%;
        }
        .loading{
            width: 80%;
            height: 25px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border: 1px solid  rgba(39, 191, 158, 1);
            border-radius: 20px;

        }
        .loading p {
            width: 10px;
            height: 25px;
            background-color: rgba(39, 191, 158, 1);
            animation: loadanimation 5s linear infinite;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0px -4px 15px 13px rgba(39, 191, 158, 0.2);
        }
        @@keyframes loadanimation {
            0%{
                width: 10px;
            }
            100%{
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
        .load_box .content {
            width: 60%;
            color: rgba(39, 191, 158, 1);
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding-top: 20px;
            animation: textanimation 3s linear infinite alternate;
        }
        @@keyframes textanimation {
            0%{
                padding-top: 20px;
            }
            100%{
                padding-top: 60px;
            }
        };
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <p>
            请使用其他浏览器打开本网站
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="load_box">
        <div class="loading">
            <p></p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h6>因内置浏览器协议问题</h6>
            <h6>请点击右上角使用其他浏览器</h6>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>